»CL9:3. Impossible »CL8:- »CL9:Loonies

»CL0:The intro welcomes us with the sign
MC68060 code by Psycho, Blueberry. I
have to admit. 060 is realy recomended
. The intro is damnly cool. A great 3D
engine was included in the 34kb, A big
number of textures compute before the
intro, a good msx. Without any doubts
a 3D intro- but a very good 3D. Intro
tested on BlizzardziePPC 040/40mhz,
64MB.. Works only on AGA :( - it
works not to smoothly.







