»CL9:6. Dive "finalversion" »CL8:- »CL9:Nah-Kolor

»CL0:A pearl for the end. Intro known to
all "Dive" by the Nah-Kolor group with
the added sign "finalversion" - if it
would take a higher locate I would be
very suprised. In my opinion the
final version isn't different from the
non final version. But.... About the
intro - intro average - some people
like it and some don't.- average - it
depends on your taste. Intro tested on
BlizzardziePPC 040/40mhz, 64MB. Works
only on AGA. :( - works smoothly.
Generally I wrote a lot about the
productions - I only forgot to add -
Not enough of them!! Such a big party,
and only a couple of productions. :(
Too bad.

»CL8:Some words for the end about
ray-tracing kompo - I haven't seen
such shit for a long time. Even the
first place is bad!!! I am sorry
,together with Ubik, that we didn't
present anything through someone,
maybe we would have earned
something...

See the stuff from The Party and tell
me one thing. Did we catch up to the
west with the level of productions or
did the west fell back to our level? I
don't want to offend anyone - it's
good that our level of productions is
improving , and is getting stronger. I
mean that what I have already
mentioned - just look on the
productions from the last years....
"SAD BUT TRUE" - the level of The
Party was much better years later than
it is right now.

